{
  "stem": "26142.11",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also in that area there was no rationing or really anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was plenty of food in the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I stayed there-- I stayed there-- be-- before-- before I, I, I, I have to backtrack a little bit.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have to tell this story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In December-- in December, I was still in, in, in Satu Mare-- yeah, in Satu Mare.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My cousin [INAUDIBLE] was alone, and she said-- she said to me, I want to go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Come with me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was very afraid to go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She says, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let's-- we'll just-- we'll just go as a couple.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We'll-- under arm-- you take me under your arm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we'll go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we went to the movies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we saw an Amer-- it was an American movie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 'Somewhere Over the Rainbow,' I remember that, that song, Judy-- Judy Garland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Judy Garland Yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyway why am I backtracking?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We got out from the movies, and on the corners of the-- of the streets, usually you had newspaper boys screaming out the latest-- the latest headlines.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And a newspaper boy-- there was a newspaper called [NON-ENGLISH] He's screaming out, the United States was attacked by the-- by the, the imperial country of Japan.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the Axis battle in Rome is now battle in Rome, Tokyo and-- And when I saw that-- so my cousin went over, and she bought a paper because I wanted to know what was-- and she told me this was December the 7th when Pearl Harbor was, was attacked.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was the happiest day in my hiding, I must admit, because I knew that the United States is going into the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
